title: Trailer Hitch Install: CURT 11350 Ford Focus
description:
This video depicts the installation of the CURT 11350 Class 1 trailer hitch on a 2014 Ford Focus. 

Install Sheet - https://www.curtmfg.com/masterlibrary/11350/installsheet/CM_11350_INS.PDF


Application Coverage:
2012 - Sedan, Hatchback
2013 - 2014 Sedan, except ST model
2013 - 2016 Hatchback, except ST and electric models
2013 - 2016 Hatchback SE with Full Body Styling Kit


Special Notes:
***DO NOT EXCEED VEHICLE MANUFACTURER'S RECOMMENDED TOWING CAPACITY***
PERIODICALLY CHECK THIS RECEIVER HITCH TO ENSURE THAT ALL FASTENERS
ARE TIGHT AND THAT ALL STRUCTURAL COMPONENTS ARE SOUND.

Warning:
-This video is intended to be used as reference. Please refer to print instructions for complete installation information.
